{"tid":2328742,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"好鍾意食辣 所以 自製辣椒油⋯⋯","createTime":"2020-12-16T17:30:59.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T14:06:08.000Z","uid":375024,"like":103,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"ad8c2e8a7384dbe1449d514dc12c1bd55dc6df7a","tid":2328742,"uid":375024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T17:30:59.000Z","msg":"家中抗武肺 悶到搵啲嘢做先<br />\n由一開始乜柒都唔識 打辣椒粉加滾油<br />\n慢慢調到合適嘅味 好有成功感<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先 洗辣椒 再矖乾 曬完 再烘<br />\n本來想人手磨 磨到唔知幾時<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n索性打成粉<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eGdYfZk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeGdYfZk.jpg&h=039d758b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mugZKSF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmugZKSF.jpg&h=cdeece94&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次用左幾種辣椒 再加滾油<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vqxVidd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvqxVidd.jpg&h=eae05814&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n完成<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72f9e54e678aa2ce48505cc99b93ac2d467cf346","tid":2328742,"uid":369015,"like":66,"dislike":0,"score":66,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T17:31:39.000Z","msg":"影得咁靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b29deca7e4621c2d85c28475fb2f9df7643977a4","tid":2328742,"uid":198035,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T17:34:57.000Z","msg":"整唔整到茶記果隻味"},{"pid":"8203d0ddaca4a274f3e1f6b30fa6b74b39676d1d","tid":2328742,"uid":341722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-16T17:37:13.000Z","msg":"用左咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":